    "2), Specificity (Eq. 3), Precision (Eq.",
    "4), F1 -Score (Eq. 5) and IoU (Eq.",
    "6) scores were calculated.",
    "IoU is defined as the measure of overlap between the actual bounding box labeled by the annotator for an object and the bounding box predicted by the model.",
